data.description: Beautiful saltwater canal home, 75' of bulkhead w/intercoastal access. Walk to the beach and restaurants. This 2 bedroom, plus flex room that can be a third bedroom or home office, 2 full bath home has many upgrades sure to please. Some recent upgrades are a new HVAC, water heater, insulated garage doors, plus beautiful privacy screen, new shed, new split unit ac/heat in the garage. Master BR w/Lg bath with huge walk-in shower, sliders to a nice deck, electric Sunbrella awning. Luxury vinyl floors throughout home, quartz countertops and stainless in the beautiful kitchen. A fully fenced yard with gorgeous landscaping giving it a park-like feel, deck, patio, hot-tub ready with pad and electric. The garage is pristine with AC/heat split unit, room for a motorcycle or golfcart. Sip your coffee and read a good book from the lanai. The Great room has a fireplace for those chilly nights. This home is a MUST SEE! All information taken from the tax record, and while deemed reliable, cannot be guaranteed.
